trans-unit.source: Provides data for the <see cref="E:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.DocumentCompleted" /> event.
trans-unit.target: Fornece dados para o evento de <see cref="E:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.DocumentCompleted" /> .

trans-unit.source: Handle the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.DocumentCompleted?displayProperty=nameWithType> event to receive notification when the new document finishes loading.
trans-unit.target: Manipular o <xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.DocumentCompleted?displayProperty=nameWithType> evento para receber notificações quando o carregamento for concluído o novo documento.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowserDocumentCompletedEventArgs> object passed to the event handler lets you retrieve the location of the new document through the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowserDocumentCompletedEventArgs.Url%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowserDocumentCompletedEventArgs> objeto passado para o manipulador de eventos permite que você recuperar o local do novo documento por meio de <xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowserDocumentCompletedEventArgs.Url%2A> propriedade.

trans-unit.source: When the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.DocumentCompleted?displayProperty=nameWithType> event occurs, the new document is fully loaded, which means you can access its contents through the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.Document%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>, <xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.DocumentText%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>, or <xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.DocumentStream%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> property.
trans-unit.target: Quando o <xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.DocumentCompleted?displayProperty=nameWithType> evento ocorrer, o novo documento totalmente é carregado, o que significa que você pode acessar seu conteúdo por meio de <xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.Document%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>, <xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.DocumentText%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>, ou <xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.DocumentStream%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> propriedade.
